The paper also discusses the management of traffic, which could fall under the category of distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). The use of optical technology for communication suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the communication and networking (cs.COMM) category. Finally, the paper discusses the development of 5G, which could fall under the category of architecture and organization (cs.AR).
